3
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,840
If you want to help Wu Dengke,

4
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,000
I suggest you go to Hang City.

5
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,200
The land Zhao Xin took

6
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,630
hasn't been surveyed.

7
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:37,630
Once he really gets it developed,

8
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,470
what the mining will become

9
00:01:40,470 --> 00:01:41,270
is hard to say.

10
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:46,270
The reason I want you to go to Hang City

11
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:47,590
is that main enterprises

12
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,840
of the NCC of Commerce are over there,

13
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:52,360
including infrastructure and shipping.

14
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,430
You'll have a place there.

15
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,000
What?

16
00:01:58,750 --> 00:02:01,000
Do you think you can move freely

17
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:03,040
because you're Zhao Xin's son?

18
00:02:08,790 --> 00:02:10,680
Even if you've broken ties
with Zhao Xin,

19
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:12,630
you're still related by blood.

20
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,630
Those people down south

21
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,950
have hated Zhao Xin for a long time.

22
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:21,400
Going to Hang City

23
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,110
could be walking into the lion's den.

24
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,360
Ms. Cai,

25
00:02:30,950 --> 00:02:31,750
thank you.

26
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:35,150
I won't reveal my identity.

27
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:35,880
There's no need.

28
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,630
There's a man you should watch out for.

29
00:02:42,150 --> 00:02:44,400
Wei Jinghai,
General Manager of Li Group.

30
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:47,240
He's a hard one to figure out.

31
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:50,040
However, someone named Fan Longquan

32
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,040
in the NCC

33
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,150
has an excellent reputation.

34
00:02:53,620 --> 00:02:55,240
You can reach out
if you have the chance.

35
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:59,310
The entire NCC isn't friendly

36
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:00,200
toward Zhao Xin.

37
00:03:02,910 --> 00:03:03,950
Be careful.

38
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,750
Qingdi didn't get along
with Zhao Xin either.

39
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,680
But once, he came back and told me

40
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:29,040
Zhao Xin went to
his trap-laden banquet alone.

41
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,750
From his expression, I could tell

42
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:35,560
he admired him.

43
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:39,910
Later on,

44
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:43,240
I met that old gentleman
at the foot of Mount Wutai

45
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,750
and shared half a cup of Hupao tea.

46
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,520
Jiadi,

47
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:57,790
you once stood at the top.

48
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,520
Even if you've fallen,

49
00:04:02,950 --> 00:04:05,310
you're willing to start over
and taste all that life offers.

50
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,750
Maybe it's a good thing.

51
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,430
Qingdi left behind a diary.

52
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:15,910
I'll lend it to you.

53
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,790
I hope you can be like him.

54
00:04:26,910 --> 00:04:29,910
Ms. Cai, there's only one Yang Qingdi

55
00:04:30,910 --> 00:04:32,000
and only one Zhao Jiadi.

56
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,000
I believe that.

57
00:04:49,150 --> 00:04:50,950
Hang City.

58
00:04:50,950 --> 00:04:52,360
Nanshan Chamber of Commerce.

59
00:04:52,910 --> 00:04:53,590
Yang Qingdi.

60
00:04:53,590 --> 00:04:54,560
Li Minxian.

61
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,270
Uncle,

62
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:58,040
you just gave me so much information.

63
00:04:58,470 --> 00:04:59,630
I just took a nap,

64
00:04:59,630 --> 00:05:01,040
and everything changed.

65
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:04,150
Wait.

66
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:05,630
The main point
of what you just said

67
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,270
is the 100,000 yuan.

68
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,240
I can't even spend it.

69
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,310
I have to return it.

70
00:05:10,790 --> 00:05:11,630
Why?

71
00:05:12,590 --> 00:05:13,040
Come on.

72
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,430
She was so straightforward.

73
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:15,520
You can't chicken out.

74
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,590
How do you know it's a "she"?

75
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:18,950
What if it's a crusty man
with stinky feet?

76
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,200
Even if it is,

77
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,630
if he gave me 100,000 yuan,

78
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:24,430
I'd still...

79
00:05:24,950 --> 00:05:25,750
No.

80
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:28,310
Wait, Uncle.

81
00:05:28,590 --> 00:05:30,270
Haven't you two known each other
for seven years?

82
00:05:30,470 --> 00:05:31,240
You've never met?

83
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,470
No.

84
00:05:32,470 --> 00:05:34,240
Then it's definitely a girl.

85
00:05:40,310 --> 00:05:41,110
Bao,

86
00:05:42,470 --> 00:05:44,110
do I still have some of that tea?

87
00:05:44,590 --> 00:05:45,400
Yeah.

88
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,750
Good, find me two cakes.

89
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,910
I'm going to visit
old school principal today.

90
00:05:48,910 --> 00:05:49,860
I can't show up empty-handed.

91
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:51,590
Got it.

92
00:05:52,050 --> 00:05:53,200
I'll get them
when I'm done.

93
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,040
Uncle,

94
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:56,430
just now,

95
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:57,910
the old school principal you've said.

96
00:05:57,910 --> 00:05:59,400
You mean the guy
with a wildflower speech?

97
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,310
Well, please tell him

98
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:03,630
his speech is so good

99
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:04,840
that has made a big impact

100
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,400
on my life.

101
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,790
I never thought

102
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:15,560
you'd say the word "life".

103
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,430
I gotta grow sometime, right?

104
00:06:19,630 --> 00:06:20,680
Uncle,

105
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:23,200
were you mocking me just now?

106
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:25,750
You even know the word "mocking" now.

107
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:26,950
Nice.

108
00:06:27,270 --> 00:06:27,880
Uncle.

109
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,000
What are you saying, Uncle?

110
00:06:29,470 --> 00:06:30,400
What are you saying?

111
00:06:30,910 --> 00:06:32,040
I'm gonna splash you.

112
00:06:32,590 --> 00:06:33,590
That's a foul.

113
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:42,680
Hei, put some inside.

114
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:06,310
Sir,

115
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:09,110
we're not open yet.

116
00:07:09,110 --> 00:07:10,200
Can you come back later?

117
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:13,560
It's fine. I'm just looking around.

118
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,950
Is your store

119
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:17,720
up for transfer?

120
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,680
I haven't heard anything
from boss about that.

121
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,270
Sorry.

122
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,910
When

123
00:07:26,910 --> 00:07:28,080
do you normally open?

124
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,400
We open at 7 p.m..

125
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:32,000
Then I'll come back later.

126
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,000
Mi,

127
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,040
bring me a bottle of champagne.

128
00:07:40,150 --> 00:07:40,430
Got it.

129
00:07:40,430 --> 00:07:41,240
Hurry up, hurry.

130
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:42,680
What's up, Bao?

131
00:07:44,910 --> 00:07:45,720
Sir.

132
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:49,000
Sorry for the trip in vain.

133
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,040
This is for you.

134
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:51,950
My treat.

135
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:53,080
No need.

136
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:54,840
It's just a bottle of wine.

137
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,470
You're welcome to come back.

138
00:08:02,470 --> 00:08:03,270
Thanks.

139
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:08,000
Drop by anytime when you're free.

140
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:12,000
Zhao,

141
00:08:12,470 --> 00:08:14,950
the fact you came to visit me

142
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:17,200
shows

143
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,110
I didn't teach you in vain.

144
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:21,200
If it weren't for your guidance,

145
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,680
I wouldn't have this perspective today.

146
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,200
You came to seek advice

147
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:27,240
[Jiang Zongxiang, retired principal]
from me.

148
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,590
Well, I think

149
00:08:29,590 --> 00:08:31,720
you should make use of your strengths

150
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:34,240
and dive into the financial sector.

151
00:08:35,430 --> 00:08:36,560
Knowledge

152
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,630
needs to be tested in practice.

153
00:08:40,630 --> 00:08:41,430
That's right.

154
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,400
Actually, I've chosen a destination.

155
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:46,110
I want to go to Hang City.

156
00:08:47,950 --> 00:08:49,750
For finance, Hai City

157
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:51,880
and Hang City are top choices.

158
00:08:52,780 --> 00:08:54,560
Are you planning
to start your own business

159
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:56,080
or join a company?

160
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,590
After what happened at Jinhai,

161
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,790
I'm not planning
to start a business for now.

162
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:03,630
Here's my think.

163
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:05,400
I wanna gain management experience
from others.

164
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:08,520
Jufeng and Risheng in Hang City

165
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:10,080
are well-known financial firms.

166
00:09:10,270 --> 00:09:12,080
They're considered leaders
in the industry.

167
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,790
I looked at their job postings.

168
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,470
The bar is quite high.

169
00:09:16,590 --> 00:09:18,110
I might not even get in.

170
00:09:18,470 --> 00:09:20,560
So, I've been looking
at other companies too.

171
00:09:21,270 --> 00:09:22,080
Young man,

172
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,590
are you belittling our school

173
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:27,310
right in front of me?

174
00:09:27,310 --> 00:09:29,680
No, I didn't mean it that way.

175
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:32,360
I wouldn't dare.

176
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:36,150
By the way, I remember Risheng has

177
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:37,950
a recommendation system, right?

178
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:39,270
Yes.

179
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:42,000
I may be retired,

180
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,630
but I still have some standing

181
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:44,470
in the industry.

182
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:47,150
If you're willing,

183
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:49,110
I can write you a recommendation letter.

184
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,880
But whether you pass the interview

185
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,590
will be up to you.

186
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,240
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

187
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,520
Mr. Jiang,

188
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,110
if you do write me a recommendation,

189
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:05,720
could you leave out my past at Jinhai?

190
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,150
Why?

191
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:10,240
Are you afraid
they'll know your background?

192
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:11,910
It's not that I'm afraid.

193
00:10:13,110 --> 00:10:15,150
I just want to rely on my own ability.

194
00:10:18,110 --> 00:10:19,270
Good.

195
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:21,750
There are

196
00:10:21,750 --> 00:10:22,720
many paths in life.

197
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,950
Each one

198
00:10:23,950 --> 00:10:25,270
has its own boundaries.

199
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:28,520
You've stuck to your boundary

200
00:10:28,560 --> 00:10:29,630
and left Jinhai.

201
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,200
That decision alone

202
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,400
means you're on the right path.

203
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:39,200
People say there are three things
to see in life.

204
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,310
First, keep vision far.

205
00:10:42,310 --> 00:10:43,290
Second, keep heart broad.

206
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,080
Third, keep mind detached.

207
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:47,560
In these few words

208
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,720
lies deep meaning.

209
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:53,240
Many stand at the foot of a mountain

210
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,240
and let the mountain

211
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,200
block their view.

212
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,840
So,

213
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:01,000
they take the mountain
as their entire world.

214
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,590
Just learning to keep vision far

215
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:07,360
can take half a lifetime of detours.

216
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:15,590
Let me give you a gift too.

217
00:11:15,750 --> 00:11:17,520
Think of it as paying you back
for the tea.

218
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:19,150
Sure.

219
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:47,840
This is for you.

220
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,200
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

221
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,840
[Way and Virtue]

222
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,880
Way and virtue.

223
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:59,680
Grandpa, I'm back.

224
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:02,520
My granddaughter's home.

225
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:03,790
Let me introduce you.

226
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:04,520
- Okay.
- Let's go.

227
00:12:05,470 --> 00:12:06,590
You're back.

228
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:08,400
We have a guest.

229
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:10,360
Yes, my favorite student,

230
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,790
Zhao Jiadi, came to visit me.

231
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,520
Come on, let me introduce you.

232
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,720
My granddaughter,

233
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,000
Jiang Tanle.

234
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,520
She also teaches at our school.

235
00:12:22,690 --> 00:12:24,430
[Jiang Tanle]
She's a teacher at our school.

236
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:27,680
Tanle means having fun in playing Go.

237
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:29,720
What do you think?

238
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,840
Not bad, right?

239
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,040
Hello, Ms. Jiang.

240
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:34,310
You two should know each other.

241
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:37,150
You probably taught

242
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:38,110
their freshman English class.

243
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:39,720
I don't just know him.

244
00:12:40,270 --> 00:12:41,790
I've heard all about him.

245
00:12:42,590 --> 00:12:43,910
I heard there was a student

246
00:12:43,910 --> 00:12:45,080
who attended every class

247
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,590
except English.

248
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,310
What happened?

249
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:49,950
After our talk,

250
00:12:49,950 --> 00:12:51,150
you still didn't go to class?

251
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:53,000
I did.

252
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:56,270
Maybe Ms. Jiang forgot me.

253
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:57,910
I went for the exam.

254
00:12:57,910 --> 00:12:58,590
Lost daily points,

255
00:12:58,590 --> 00:12:59,720
but I didn't fail.

256
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:02,880
I saw his paper.

257
00:13:03,310 --> 00:13:04,270
He did quite well.

258
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:06,360
Grandpa, you two keep chatting.

259
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,910
I'll go cook.

260
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,470
Mr. Jiang, you get some rest.

261
00:13:10,470 --> 00:13:11,910
I'll head out.

262
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:12,590
No way.

263
00:13:12,590 --> 00:13:13,840
You have to stay for dinner.

264
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:14,790
I was even thinking

265
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:16,080
of playing a few rounds with you.

266
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,200
Always losing to you

267
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,430
is getting a bit embarrassing.

268
00:13:19,430 --> 00:13:20,040
Grandpa,

269
00:13:20,750 --> 00:13:23,110
with your skills, you still lose to him?

270
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:24,560
You don't know this.

271
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:26,000
In my opinion,

272
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,680
Zhao's skills

273
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:28,840
are on par with Lin Peng's.

274
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,310
We're talking about Go.

275
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:32,630
Why bring him up?

276
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:35,400
Come on, Zhao.

277
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:36,430
Move that table over here.

278
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:37,470
Okay.

279
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:40,680
Get a stool.

280
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:48,520
Let's agree on this first.

281
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:50,150
You're better than me,

282
00:13:50,430 --> 00:13:51,720
so I can make five moves first.

283
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:52,680
No problem.

284
00:13:52,910 --> 00:13:54,200
Then I won't hold back.

285
00:13:54,310 --> 00:13:55,560
I'll take black and start first.

286
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:57,080
Okay.

287
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:28,910
Chen, the fruit is on me.

288
00:14:31,430 --> 00:14:32,910
After the renovation,

