299
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:05,200
Shui's here.

300
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:06,950
Long time no see.

301
00:15:06,950 --> 00:15:08,400
Go and have a drink.

302
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:12,830
Hello?

303
00:15:13,990 --> 00:15:14,830
Hello, Uncle.

304
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:15,830
Hello, Bao.

305
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:17,560
