to take care of there.

327
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:30,830
If you're around,

328
00:16:31,470 --> 00:16:33,040
do you want to meet up?

329
00:16:34,630 --> 00:16:36,150
Don't get me wrong.

330
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:38,720
