I wanna discuss with you in person.

331
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:46,760
I just saw your message.
I'm in Hai City.

332
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:49,350
We can meet. I'll send you my number.

333
00:16:52,830 --> 00:16:54,510
I do have the map. Here it is.

334
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:55,470
Thanks.

335
00:16:57,310 --> 00:16:59,080
Wei Jinghai

336
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:00,240
contacted me again

337
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:02,120
and said he wanted you

338
00:17:02,510 --> 00:17:03,880
to meet Cai Yanzhi.

339
00:17:03,880 --> 00:17:04,400
No.

340
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:11,470
Nalan Changsheng

341
00:17:11,470 --> 00:17:12,670
and Wei Mingyi

342
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:14,120
are like half a benefactor to me.

343
00:17:14,630 --> 00:17:16,670
It's only out of respect for them

344
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:19,120
that I let people call me by my name.

345
00:17:20,080 --> 00:17:22,560
But I really don't like Wei Jinghai.

346
00:17:28,990 --> 00:17:30,920
Wei Mingyi was a kind man,

347
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,630
but he was unlucky.

348
00:17:33,350 --> 00:17:35,630
His son is nothing like him.

349
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:37,880
He's always going on

350
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,600
