351
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:41,560
His head

352
00:17:41,670 --> 00:17:43,040
is full of schemes.

353
00:18:14,630 --> 00:18:15,880
You didn't reply for so long.

354
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,280
I thought you didn't want to see me.

355
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:18,880
I'm already in Hai City.

356
00:18:19,040 --> 00:18:20,310
