358
00:18:27,150 --> 00:18:27,760
Okay.

359
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,190
I can't refuse the favor.

360
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:31,190
I'm heading to M Bar.

361
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:32,280
I'll send you the address.

362
00:18:44,310 --> 00:18:45,120
Sure.

363
00:18:45,470 --> 00:18:47,120
Just a heads-up.

364
00:18:47,120 --> 00:18:48,040
I'm not good-looking,

365
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:49,510
