366
00:18:51,040 --> 00:18:53,310
It's fine. We're about the same.

367
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:03,830
Bro, they're arguing over there.

368
00:19:06,790 --> 00:19:08,400
Grab a bottle from the bar.

369
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,040
Got it.

370
00:19:13,990 --> 00:19:15,400
Wei Jinghai said

371
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,600
