375
00:19:23,760 --> 00:19:25,400
He can't help with that.

376
00:19:25,670 --> 00:19:27,240
If he comes to you again,

377
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:28,920
just say a few polite words.

378
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:30,920
I don't want to get involved.

379
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:31,760
Got it?

380
00:19:32,120 --> 00:19:33,120
Why are you so unreasonable?

381
00:19:33,120 --> 00:19:33,920
You little punk.

382
00:19:34,830 --> 00:19:35,920
