383
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:37,510
Come on, sit down.

384
00:19:37,830 --> 00:19:38,720
Please sit down.

385
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:39,950
Come on, sit down.

386
00:19:39,990 --> 00:19:41,630
