387
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,080
Please calm down.

388
00:19:43,190 --> 00:19:44,080
Please don't

389
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:45,990
hold it against them for my sake, okay?

390
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:49,080
You're just a waiter.

391
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:50,720
Why should I listen to you?

392
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:53,600
Get lost.

393
00:19:55,080 --> 00:19:56,280
Or I'll trash your bar.

394
00:19:56,750 --> 00:19:58,040
Sorry for speaking out of turn.

395
00:19:58,280 --> 00:20:00,120
I'm just a waiter.
I mean nothing to you,

396
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:00,830
right?

397
00:20:01,150 --> 00:20:02,600
Sir, we're here to have fun,

398
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:04,280
so we have to enjoy ourselves, right?

399
00:20:06,470 --> 00:20:07,510
This wine

400
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:08,760
is on me.

401
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:10,760
Let me toast to you, okay?

402
00:20:16,510 --> 00:20:18,040
I'll stop when you want me to.

403
00:20:20,310 --> 00:20:21,120
Giving me wine?

404
00:20:23,350 --> 00:20:25,240
Do you think I'm short on wine?

405
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:32,630
Do you think I'm short on wine

406
00:20:32,630 --> 00:20:33,990
or money?

407
00:20:35,350 --> 00:20:36,240
I see.

408
00:20:38,470 --> 00:20:40,310
You want to stand up for them, huh?

409
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:42,400
Fine.

410
00:20:43,350 --> 00:20:44,150
Here.

411
00:20:44,830 --> 00:20:45,630
See this?

412
00:20:45,670 --> 00:20:47,080
Drink all this wine,

413
00:20:47,080 --> 00:20:48,630
and we'll call it even.

414
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,150
- Pour the wine.
- Pour it!

415
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:51,990
Fill it up.

416
00:20:52,350 --> 00:20:53,670
Drink all of it.

417
00:20:54,510 --> 00:20:55,240
Pour it.

418
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:56,920
Hurry. Pour the wine.

419
00:20:57,310 --> 00:20:58,120
Pour it.

420
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,240
Be quick.

421
00:21:14,760 --> 00:21:17,080
Drink every drop of the wine
on the table,

422
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,920
and I'll let it go.

423
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:21,150
Pour the wine. Drink up.

424
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,040
Bao.

425
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:30,240
Buddy.

426
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:32,120
That's enough.

427
00:21:32,150 --> 00:21:33,040
Don't go too far.

428
00:21:35,510 --> 00:21:36,510
Is this too far?

429
00:21:40,310 --> 00:21:41,310
Is this too far?

430
00:21:42,990 --> 00:21:43,600
Sir,

431
00:21:43,990 --> 00:21:45,240
I'll drink.

432
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:45,760
Is that okay?

433
00:21:46,280 --> 00:21:47,080
Drink it.

434
00:21:47,080 --> 00:21:48,280
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

435
00:21:48,720 --> 00:21:49,920
Did you hear that?

436
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:51,440
He's drinking voluntarily.

437
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,400
I didn't force him.

438
00:21:52,950 --> 00:21:53,830
Got it?

439
00:21:54,350 --> 00:21:55,440
I'll be back soon and drink.

440
00:21:55,670 --> 00:21:56,670
Is that okay?

441
00:21:56,670 --> 00:21:57,630
Sit.

442
00:21:59,150 --> 00:21:59,950
Uncle.

443
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:01,240
Go away.

444
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:03,350
- What are you doing?
- What are you looking at?

445
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:06,040
Uncle,

446
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,400
this is my job.

447
00:22:07,670 --> 00:22:08,600
I have to drink.

448
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:09,950
Wait for me here.

449
00:22:09,990 --> 00:22:11,150
I'll go get your keys.

450
00:22:34,790 --> 00:22:35,600
- Drink up.
- Drink.

451
00:22:36,190 --> 00:22:37,120
Come on, drink.

452
00:22:37,190 --> 00:22:38,510
Drink. Drink. Come on.

453
00:22:39,120 --> 00:22:40,280
Keep going. Don't stop. Drink.

454
00:22:40,630 --> 00:22:41,440
Drink. Drink.

455
00:22:42,120 --> 00:22:43,400
Come on, drink.

456
00:22:43,420 --> 00:22:44,510
Aren't you good at drinking?

457
00:22:44,880 --> 00:22:45,830
Don't you want to drink?

458
00:22:45,990 --> 00:22:46,920
Come on, drink.

459
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,790
- Come on.
- Drink.

460
00:22:51,560 --> 00:22:52,990
- Drink.
- Drink.

461
00:22:56,040 --> 00:22:57,120
Come on, drink.

462
00:23:00,510 --> 00:23:01,310
Good.

463
00:23:02,040 --> 00:23:03,120
- Good.
- Good.

464
00:23:04,350 --> 00:23:05,600
Don't stop.

465
00:23:05,600 --> 00:23:06,040
Drink.

466
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:07,950
Drink up. I'll help you out.

467
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:08,630
Let me help you.

468
00:23:12,830 --> 00:23:13,670
Come on.

469
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:31,190
I'll drink for him.

470
00:23:40,280 --> 00:23:41,040
Another one.

471
00:23:41,040 --> 00:23:42,120
Another one who can drink.

472
00:23:42,720 --> 00:23:43,720
You upset me earlier.

473
00:23:45,150 --> 00:23:46,720
You're drinking for him, right? Fine.

474
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:50,240
You drink this.

475
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:05,280
- Drink.
- If you're going to drink, drink this.

476
00:24:08,470 --> 00:24:09,600
Let me give you some advice.

477
00:24:10,790 --> 00:24:12,440
A man should live with dignity.

478
00:24:14,470 --> 00:24:15,880
Don't hurt others' dignity.

479
00:24:19,310 --> 00:24:20,400
You're lecturing me now?

480
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:21,880
You want dignity?

481
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:23,510
Fine.

482
00:24:25,310 --> 00:24:26,670
I'll give you that dignity.

483
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:52,510
Get him.

484
00:24:53,950 --> 00:24:54,400
Who?

485
00:24:54,950 --> 00:24:55,630
Bro.

486
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:15,310
Come on.

487
00:25:15,980 --> 00:25:16,790
Do you want to smoke?

488
00:25:24,310 --> 00:25:25,240
Boss,

489
00:25:25,560 --> 00:25:27,240
