492
00:25:51,600 --> 00:25:53,120
When you're under someone,

493
00:25:54,100 --> 00:25:55,560
you've got to treat yourself
like a human.

494
00:25:57,470 --> 00:25:58,790
When you're above someone,

495
00:25:59,470 --> 00:26:00,990
you've got to treat others like humans.

496
00:26:14,310 --> 00:26:16,040
Don't you agree?

497
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:22,240
These young men

498
00:26:22,560 --> 00:26:23,790
are my friends.

499
00:26:24,600 --> 00:26:26,240
So, I'd appreciate it

500
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:27,950
if you could let them go

501
00:26:28,510 --> 00:26:29,560
for my sake.

502
00:26:29,950 --> 00:26:30,990
Is that okay?

503
00:26:35,350 --> 00:26:36,150
I'm sorry.

504
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:52,350
Chen.

505
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:06,280
Sit here.

506
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:11,400
Thanks.

507
00:27:12,190 --> 00:27:13,280
I'm Zhao Jiadi.

508
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:16,640
Chen Fusheng.

509
00:27:21,120 --> 00:27:22,440
I don't smoke.

510
00:27:23,280 --> 00:27:24,350
You can keep that for now.

511
00:27:24,920 --> 00:27:25,600
We'll meet again

512
00:27:25,600 --> 00:27:26,550
sometime.

513
00:27:26,620 --> 00:27:27,890
Just give me
something else in return.

514
00:29:04,620 --> 00:29:05,760
[You have 6 missed calls.]
Oh no.

515
00:29:05,760 --> 00:29:07,030
I forgot about her.

516
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:11,320
Sorry, sorry.

517
00:29:11,320 --> 00:29:12,300
My friend was hospitalized last night.

518
00:29:12,870 --> 00:29:14,760
I didn't mean to stand you up.

519
00:30:00,760 --> 00:30:01,550
Hello?

520
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:07,870
Hello?

521
00:30:14,710 --> 00:30:15,510
Hello?

522
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:20,830
Hello?

523
00:30:23,030 --> 00:30:23,830
Hello?

524
00:30:24,990 --> 00:30:26,760
Did you get my message?

525
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:29,480
Sorry about yesterday.

526
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:31,960
It was kind of sudden with my friend.

527
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:33,440
I didn't get to tell you earlier.

528
00:30:36,800 --> 00:30:37,920
Is he doing better now?

529
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:43,440
Your friend?

530
00:30:43,870 --> 00:30:45,350
Didn't you say he's in the hospital?

531
00:30:48,080 --> 00:30:49,390
Luckily, we got him here in time.

532
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:51,100
He got his stomach pumped
and got an IV.

533
00:30:51,870 --> 00:30:53,280
Now he's snoring,

534
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:54,510
strong as ever.

535
00:30:54,990 --> 00:30:56,350
The doctor said he's fine.

536
00:30:57,280 --> 00:30:59,280
I waited for you for hours yesterday.

537
00:31:00,260 --> 00:31:01,670
I thought maybe you didn't wait for me

538
00:31:01,670 --> 00:31:02,550
and went in first,

539
00:31:02,550 --> 00:31:03,870
so you couldn't hear your phone ringing.

540
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:07,550
Why didn't you come and find me?

541
00:31:07,550 --> 00:31:08,710
If you'd come to find me,

542
00:31:09,030 --> 00:31:11,190
you'd have seen me drinking

543
00:31:11,190 --> 00:31:12,000
with a group of beauties.

544
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:14,160
I don't believe it.

545
00:31:14,710 --> 00:31:16,990
Maybe you can fool the young girls.

546
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:20,510
So, you're not young anymore?

547
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,080
Sorry about that, ma'am.

548
00:31:23,120 --> 00:31:23,960
I'm hanging up.

549
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:26,190
Just kidding.

550
00:31:28,870 --> 00:31:29,990
Do you have time today?

551
00:31:30,390 --> 00:31:31,830
I want to make it up to you

552
00:31:32,030 --> 00:31:33,760
and talk about the project
you mentioned.

553
00:31:34,990 --> 00:31:36,160
What?

554
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:37,920
No project means no apology?

555
00:31:39,080 --> 00:31:40,550
That's nonsense.

556
00:31:41,190 --> 00:31:42,710
How about I treat you to dinner?

557
00:31:43,710 --> 00:31:44,870
But I have to warn you.

558
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:48,030
I'm a bit broke lately.

559
00:31:48,320 --> 00:31:50,600
I'll pay, but you'll have to settle

560
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:52,640
for anything.

561
00:31:53,710 --> 00:31:55,480
Meet at 5 p.m..
Send me the address.

562
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:59,710
Alright, I'll get there early this time.

563
00:31:59,710 --> 00:32:01,990
I'll wait even if it's raining knives
from the sky.

564
00:32:02,080 --> 00:32:03,480
If you don't come, I won't leave.

565
00:32:28,710 --> 00:32:30,230
Hello?

566
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:31,480
Waiting for a long time?

567
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:32,710
I'm almost there.

568
00:32:32,710 --> 00:32:35,760
It's only been two hours.

569
00:32:36,120 --> 00:32:37,320
Didn't we agree on 5 p.m.?

570
00:32:37,320 --> 00:32:38,830
I've been watching the time.

571
00:32:39,280 --> 00:32:40,480
Just kidding.

572
00:32:42,350 --> 00:32:43,670
There's quite a crowd now.

573
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:46,160
Do you want me to pick something up

574
00:32:46,390 --> 00:32:47,640
